These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, kale, pepper, radish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, october, may
House: palace, townhouse, gothic-revival, cottage
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating radish is on the right of the palace house##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 4. the palace house is not the person eating radish##6
 5. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
 6. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the person eating kale##8
 8. the person eating kale is not the cottage house##6
 9. the person eating apple is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
10. the townhouse house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person eating kale is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
12. the person eating kale is in an even position##4
13. the person eating radish is not to the right of the cottage house##8
14. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | apple         | radish     | pepper     | kale         |
| Birthday   | april | may    | october     | september |
| House   | palace       | townhouse | cottage | gothic-revival       |

