.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, milk, water
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, cat, hedgehog
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, february, december
 1. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 2. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person drinking water is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is not the person drinking milk##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk          | coffee      | water      | iced-tea   |
| Pet        | cat     | mouse | chinchilla | hedgehog      |
| Birthday      | december | july    | june  | february |

