.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, satire, comedy, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, d&b, techno
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, brown, apricot
 1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
 5. the person who likes light-blue is not the fan of blues##6
 6. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the fan of blues is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
10. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy  | satire | sports | romance |
| Music-Genre   | country  | blues      | techno | d&b        |
| Color     | light-blue | brown       | apricot    | fuchsia     |

