The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, jazz, pop
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite, lily, marigold
 1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 3. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the person who growsaconite##8
 6. the person who growslily is not to the right of the person traveling to venice##8
 7. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
 8. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the person who growsaconite##5
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growslily##1
10. the person traveling to venice is the person who growslily##1
11. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| City   | san-francisco   | venice | rome    | london |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | folk     | dubstep   | pop     |
| Flower   | zinnia | lily   | aconite | marigold    |

