.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, purple, light-blue, mauve
4 different pets are kept: dog, snake, pony, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, lacrosse, snowboarding
 1. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 2. the person who likes purple is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 3. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
 5. the person who likes purple is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is not the person who likes light-blue##6
 7. the person who likes pink is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
 8. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the person who likes pink##8
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who likes light-blue##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the owner of the pony##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color         | light-blue       | pink | purple  | mauve    |
| Pet   | pony       | mouse    | snake | dog    |
| Sport         | snowboarding | baseball   | lacrosse   | basketball |

