.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, grapes, plum, potato
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, may, november
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, grey, ebony, yellow
 1. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is not the person who likes grey##6
 3. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person who's birthday is in november##7
 4. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the person who likes ebony is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 8. the person who likes yellow is between the person eating blueberry and the person who likes ebony##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
10. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating potato##8
11. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | grapes      | plum      | potato | blueberry |
| Birthday   | may | august    | november | october     |
| Color   | amber    | ebony | yellow  | grey |

