 3. the person eating cabbage is between the person eating potato and the person who likes light-blue##2
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is not the person eating asparagus##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
 9. the person eating asparagus is not to the left of the person who likes light-blue##8
10. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person eating asparagus##8
12. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5

