.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, february, january
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, jet-ski, roller, train
1. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in february##7
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
7. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person drinking fanta##7
9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | coffee | iced-tea  | soy-milk |
| Birthday          | december | january   | september | february |
| Transport   | motorbike     | jet-ski   | train      | roller      |

