.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, pilot, librarian, photographer
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indonesian, malaysian, pakistani
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, tea, soy-milk
 1. the librarian is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
 2. the pakistani is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the malaysian##7
 3. the pilot is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 5. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the german is not to the left of the librarian##8
 7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the german is somewhere to the right of the software-developer##5
 9. the pilot is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
10. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the pilot##8
11. the german is not to the left of the photographer##8
12. the pilot is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
13. the german is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5
14. the photographer is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Job         | software-developer    | librarian | photographer | pilot    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | pakistani    | german      | indonesian |
| Beverage     | fanta | cola          | soy-milk      | tea       |

