House: victorian, art-deco, modern, gothic-revival
 1. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
 2. the coach is not the person eating cauliflower##6
 3. the mechanic is the person eating cabbage##1
 4. the coach is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
 5. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the architect##3
 6. the modern house is the coach##1
 7. the bartender is not to the right of the coach##8
 8. the coach is not to the left of the person eating artichoke##8
 9. the coach is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
10. the coach is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
11. the architect is not the person eating cabbage##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food      | grapefruit     | artichoke  | cabbage | cauliflower |
| Job           | bartender | coach | mechanic | architect   |
| House   | gothic-revival | modern  | art-deco   | victorian   |

