 5. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 6. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 7. the tower house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 8. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the right of the cottage house##8
