.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, trike, airplane
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, rabbit, snake
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, february, december
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the snake##2
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
